flowchart LR
    A[Freeze current JSON changes] --> B[Back up repo data and live site]
    B --> C[Inventory JSON, GeoJSON, route outputs and payment links]
    C --> D[Create PostgreSQL + PostGIS]
    D --> E[Create migration tables and import scripts]
    E --> F[Import passengers, locations and schedules]
    F --> G[Validate counts and spot-check records]
    G --> H[Connect existing schedule and route logic to DB reads]
    H --> I[Run old and new systems in parallel]
    I --> J{Parity checks pass?}
    J -- No --> K[Fix mappings and rerun]
    K --> G
    J -- Yes --> L[Switch application reads to database]
    L --> M[Keep JSON export as rollback snapshot]
    M --> N[Smoke test live site]
    N --> O{Critical failure?}
    O -- Yes --> P[Rollback to static JSON]
    O -- No --> Q[Migration complete]
